Orquesta Típica Victor

"CD-Discography" of 463 recordings by Orquesta Típica Victor and CDs containing them.

According to discographies following recordings are missing:

  • El rancho de Don José, Ranchera, 1943
  • Guarda la luna, Pasodoble, 1927
  • La canción del ukelele, Foxtrot, 1926
  • Una mirada, singer: Roberto Díaz, Tango, 1930

 

This listing is not a discography, but giving information on which CD you can find the recordings being listed in discographies. It is based on my private tango collection of CDs by major music labels, tango clubs and collectors.

In case of Orquesta Típica Victor sometimes it is difficult to know if a certain recording should be listed as recording by Orquesta Típica Victor since various formations recorded for the music label Victor. Therefore some discographies might list or miss certain recordings.

In case you found missing or wrong information, or you might be able to help finding missing tracks - any feedback is very much welcomed! You may get in contact with me, or leave your comment at the end of this page.

If you are interested in one of the CDs mentioned get in contact with me, I might be able to get it for you. Of course you are also welcomed to take a look at my CDs on sale.

Please find more information about Orquesta Típica Victor at Todotango.com.
